><sup>2</sup> + <i>b</i><sup>2</sup></span>.)</figcaption></figure>
<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"Rearrangement_proofs">Rearr=
angement proofs</h3></div>
<p>In one rearrangement proof, two squares are used whose sides have a meas=
ure of <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class=
=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><=
math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\displaystyle=
 a+b}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle=3D"true" scriptlevel=3D"0">
        <mi>a</mi>
        <mo>+</mo>
        <mi>b</mi>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle a+b}</annotat=
ion>
  </semantics>
