</p><p>The first result equates the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wik=
i/Cosine" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Cosine">cosines</a> of the angles =
<span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">=CE=B8</span>, wh=
ereas the second result equates their <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w=
iki/Sine" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Sine">sines</a>.
</p><p>These ratios can be written as
<span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=3D"mwe-=
math-mathml-display mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math di=
