ed}BC^{2}&amp;=3DAB\times BH,\\AC^{2}&amp;=3DAB\times AH.\end{aligned}}}</a=
nnotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/e3c18f8d2cb8fd65782f83f01d76b0fc6b2c0244" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-display mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertica=
l-align: -2.505ex; width:19.288ex; height:6.176ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle {=
\begin{aligned}BC^{2}&amp;=3DAB\times BH,\\AC^{2}&amp;=3DAB\times AH.\end{a=
ligned}}}"></span>
Summing these two equalities results in
<span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=3D"mwe-=
math-mathml-display mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math di=
