t=3D"270" class=3D"mw-file-element" data-file-width=3D"500" data-file-heigh=
t=3D"540"></a><figcaption>Illustration including the new lines</figcaption>=
</figure>
<figure class=3D"mw-default-size" typeof=3D"mw:File/Thumb"><a href=3D"https=
