ram for differential proof</figcaption></figure>
<p>If <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">x</span> is=
 increased by a small amount <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-sty=
le:italic;">dx</span> by extending the side <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" st=
