 {sgn} (\alpha +\beta -\gamma )=3D\operatorname {sgn} (a^{2}+b^{2}-c^{2}),}=
</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
