=3D"texhtml">(3, 4, 5),</span> <span class=3D"texhtml">(5, 12, 13),</span> =
<span class=3D"texhtml">(7, 24, 25),</span> <span class=3D"texhtml">(8, 15,=
 17),</span> <span class=3D"texhtml">(9, 40, 41),</span> <span class=3D"tex=
