tml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">z</span> to the origin.</figcaption>=
</figure>
<p>For any <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Complex_number" title=
=3D"Complex number">complex number</a>
<span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=3D"mwe-=
math-mathml-display mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math di=
