<p>At any selected angle of a general triangle of sides <span class=3D"texh=
tml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">a</span>, <span class=3D"texhtml mva=
r" style=3D"font-style:italic;">b</span>, <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" styl=
