ppose the selected angle <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:i=
talic;">=CE=B8</span> is opposite the side labeled <span class=3D"texhtml m=
var" style=3D"font-style:italic;">c</span>. Inscribing the isosceles triang=
le forms triangle <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;"=
