on"><img src=3D"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/2d/P=
ythagoras_3d.svg/250px-Pythagoras_3d.svg.png" decoding=3D"async" width=3D"1=
90" height=3D"190" class=3D"mw-file-element" data-file-width=3D"512" data-f=
ile-height=3D"512"></a><figcaption>Pythagoras's theorem in three dimensions=
 relates the diagonal AD to the three sides.</figcaption></figure>
<figure class=3D"mw-default-size" typeof=3D"mw:File/Thumb"><a href=3D"https=
