cription"><img src=3D"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/=
b/b4/Tetrahedron_vertfig.svg/250px-Tetrahedron_vertfig.svg.png" decoding=3D=
"async" width=3D"190" height=3D"190" class=3D"mw-file-element" data-file-wi=
dth=3D"600" data-file-height=3D"600"></a><figcaption>A tetrahedron with out=
ward facing right-angle corner</figcaption></figure>
<p>In terms of <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Solid_geometry" tit=
