style:italic;">n</span>-dimensional Pythagorean theorem":<sup id=3D"cite_re=
f-Bhatia_52-0" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki=
/Pythagorean_theorem#cite_note-Bhatia-52"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</s=
pan>51<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup>
</p>
