tps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pythagorean_theorem#cite_note-64"><span class=
=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>63<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup>
<span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=3D"mwe-=
