-image-display mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertica=
l-align: -3.338ex; width:20.362ex; height:7.176ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle d=
s^{2}=3D\sum _{i,j}^{n}g_{ij}\,dx_{i}\,dx_{j}}"></span>
</p><p>which is called the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Metric_=
